Share information
Cube Storage Pioneers

Little Robots, Big Business

Since its inception in 1996, AutoStore™ has worked to improve warehouse efficiency. Today, the company’s key value proposition is to deliver an easy-to-use software powered cubic automatic storage and retrieval ecosystem.

The AutoStore solution is modular and flexible, and can automate any warehouse. The system offers a superior customer value proposition across operating metrics, ESG scores, and customer economics.
‍

View video to learn more

elements.contents: ... that Chronicles from the Land of the Happiest People on Earth was Wole Soyinka's first novel in nearly fifty years?

elements.contents: ... that cricketer William O'Rourke has the best match-bowling figures by a New Zealander on a Test debut?

elements.contents: ... that Biodiversity Impact Credits seek to stop species extinction?

elements.title: Palestinian press (Wikipedia — did you know?)

elements.title: Cameron Butler (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that ice hockey player Cameron Butler "had the good fortune not to get pulled over as he raced" to reach his team's game in time for his NHL debut?

elements.contents: ... that the iZombie episode "And He Shall Be a Good Man" gets its name from an Elton John lyric?
